NGINX SET-UP AND CONFIGURATION


STEP-1


Download and install nginx

$ sudo apt-get install nginx


STEP-2


Configuring nginx

$ cd /etc/nginx
$ cd sites-available
$ sudo vi default


STEP-3


Find
-root /var/www/example.com;

Change to path to your folder

eg:-
-root /home/mohit/Desktop/numadic;


STEP-4


Find
listen 80;
listen [::]:80;

Change port as you want

eg:-
listen 3000;
listen [::]:3000;


STEP-5


After changing, restart the service
$ sudo service nginx restart
